  "title": "谷歌 AI 封神五年！AlphaFold 狂揽诺奖，2 亿蛋白结构全预测",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652649420&idx=2&sn=f33cf4dc80612a23937a59b1d0029b83",
  "date": "2025-11-27 04:10:00",
  "author": "新智元",
